                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>This curse affects only humanoids. <strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"19\" data-pf2-traits=\"curse,necromancy,primal\" data-pf2-label=\"Curse of the Werewolf DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save. On each full moon, the cursed creature must succeed at another Fortitude save or turn into a werewolf until dawn. The creature is under the GM's control and goes on a rampage for half the night before falling unconscious until dawn.</p>"
